What you need to know:

Their last opportunity arrived on 65 minutes but Alexander Sorloth's header from a cross by Hee-Chan Hwang spun over Alisson's fingertips only to rebound out from the bar.Soon after Salah and Mane ruthlessly punished the let-off by securing Liverpool's berth in the last eight.In the 70th minute the Egyptian fired a spot past Gulacsi, then four minutes later Mane turned a cross by substitute Divock Origi past the hapless Hungarian.